<HEADLINE>
<P>
HERE IS A SURE WAY TO END ILLEGAL PAYMENTS 
</P>
</HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
<P>
There's one sure way to halt the seemingly endless illegal payment scandals in 
college athletics: Make the payments legal. 
</P>
<P>
As it stands, student-athletes are not allowed to share in any of the huge 
revenues they often help bring in for their schools. 
</P>
<P>
Nobody objects to students getting paid for working in the university bookstore 
or cafeteria. So why shouldn't their classmates be rewarded for their athletic 
skills and effort? 
</P>
<P>
Only a few are able to go on to earn a living as professional athletes. It's 
time to cut the hypocrisy and catch up to the real world. 
</P>
<P>
ARLEN GROSSMAN 
</P>
<P>
Los Angeles 
</P>
