<P>
INAUGURATIONS; BUSH, GEORGE; BUSH, BARBARA; FAMILIES; PRESIDENT (U.S.); UNITED 
STATES -- CELEBRATIONS 
</P>
</SUBJECT>
</DOC>
<DOC>
<DOCNO> LA012189-0073 </DOCNO>
<DOCID> 8221 </DOCID>
<DATE>
<P>
January 21, 1989, Saturday, Home Edition 
</P>
