SACRAMENTO FILE 
</P>
</HEADLINE>
<BYLINE>
<P>
Compiled by Jerry Gillam, Times staff writer 
</P>
</BYLINE>
<TEXT>
<P>
Governor 
</P>
<P>
Will travel to Europe on Wednesday to meet with West German Chancellor Helmut 
Kohl and address the World Economic Forum in Davos, Switzerland. The governor 
will return to California on Feb. 5. 
</P>
<P>
Assembly 
</P>
<P>
