<HEADLINE>
<P>
NIBBLES AND BITS 
</P>
</HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
<P>
The Bowers Museum Shop reopens Sunday at its new location, 2036 N. Main St., 
Santa Ana. Shop hours will be noon to 5 Sundays and Saturdays, 10 a.m. to 5 
p.m. Tuesdays through Fridays. 
</P>
<P>
The Grove Theatre Company has announced receipt of a grant of $2,500 from the 
Orange County Register. 
</P>
